                    By Clicking Submit, I agree to have read and understood the @Html.ActionLink("Terms and Conditions", "TermsAndCondition")
                    and @Html.ActionLink("Privacy Policy", "PrivacyPolicy") of E_HealthCare & give my consent to contact me.
                </span>

